NAME = $(shell basename $(shell pwd))
PATCH = browser/${NAME}.patch
TWEAKS = browser/${NAME}.json
TITLE = Sharing Super Mix
DESCRIPTION = This patch is a combined version of various patches which allow you to share webpages through apps. It is based on work by Thomas Coe, fritos1406, @benyfish, and @semicolonapps.<br/><br/>Supports: Neato, Spare Time, Relego, ReKindleIt!, Facebook (Catalog/Beta), Bad Kitty, Spaz SpEd/Beta/Free, Twee, Tweed, Carbon (official), Quick Post.<br/><br/>Adds gesture commands and separates Share Page into Share Via Email/SMS (SMS share auto-shortens URL).<br/><br/>Options shown are configured via the Tweaks application.<br/><br/>For more info on the various options, see the corresponding help in the Tweaks app.<br/><br/>Update: Added Facebook beta, changed Spaz launch order, fixed Carbon, added Quick Post, moved Private Browsing to the Behavior and Options Tweaks patch. Resets your preferences.
CATEGORY = Browser
